Over the years, I have gained hands-on experience designing cloud-native architectures, real-time multi-user platforms, and robust data pipelines, while working in fast-paced environments and startups. I have optimized backends, automated workflows, and ensured that the software I build delivers tangible impact for both users and organizations. My projects have ranged from creating innovative applications that demonstrate new possibilities like quantum networking, to designing core systems that handle large-scale operations with speed and precision. I am adept at collaborating with diverse teams to achieve shared goals and am passionate about contributing to a culture of continuous improvement.

Beyond professional work, I enjoy exploring diverse domainsfrom AI and machine learning to distributed systemsand contributing to open-source projects. I am driven by a continuous learning mindset, collaborating with talented peers, and taking on challenges that push me to grow, innovate, and create software that makes a difference.
